      <title>GT <replaceable role="entity">version</replaceable>: Data Management Components</title>
      <titleabbrev>Data Management</titleabbrev>
      <para>Data management tools are concerned with the location, transfer, and management of
            distributed data.</para>
      <para>See <olink targetdoc="dataKey"/> for more important high-level information about data management components.</para>
      <informaltable frame="none">
            <tgroup cols="2">
